price: Toltuuwwan isaaniif ariifachiifna (se'uu?) Lakkii; (Nuti kanaaf hin goone) Garuu isaan hin hubatan.
arabic: نُسَارِعُ لَهُمۡ فِي ٱلۡخَيۡرَٰتِۚ بَل لَّا يَشۡعُرُونَ

version.title: Oromo translation
version.description: Translation of the Quran meanings into Oromo by Ghaly Ababour Abaghuna, printed in 2009.

meta.transliteration: nusāriʿu lahum fī al-khayrāti bal lā yashʿurūna
